@startuml
title Deployment Diagram - Edge AI Conveyor Monitoring

node "Production Line" as Line {
  node "Production Line Cameras" as Cameras
}

node "Edge Server\nEdge Computing" as Edge {
  component "Video Stream Processor" as VSP
  component "AI Inference Service\nComputer Vision Model" as AIS
  component "Robot Command Service" as RCS
}

node "Robot Controller" as RC
node "Robot Manipulator" as Robot
database "Central Database" as DB

node "Operator Workstation" as Workstation {
  artifact "Operator Web Dashboard" as Dashboard
}

Cameras --> VSP : Video Stream
VSP --> AIS : Frames
AIS --> RCS : Defect event
RCS --> RC : Control command
RC --> Robot : Remove defective item

AIS --> DB : Defect image + metadata
RCS --> DB : Action result
DB --> Dashboard : Analytics and reports
Dashboard --> DB : Query history

note right of Edge
Edge Computing нужен для минимальной задержки
и обработки видео рядом с производственной линией.
end note
@enduml
